bbr title=\"15th Conference of the Parties\">COP15</abbr>), before going on to work at the Department for Energy and Climate Change (<abbr title=\"Department for Energy and Climate Change\">DECC</abbr>).</p>\n\n<p>She was previously Executive Director at WWF-UK.</p>\n\n<p>She was awarded an OBE for her services to tackling climate change.</p>\n\n","image":{"url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/69933abf492ea446ea7f44ac/s465_katie-white-960.png"}},"document_type":"person","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2025-10-10T15:23:44Z","schema_name":"person","title":"Katie White OBE MP","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/government/people/katie-white","withdrawn":false}],"role":[{"api_path":"/api/content/government/ministers/parliamentary-under-secretary-of-state-minister-for-climate","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/ministers/parliamentary-under-secretary-of-state-minister-for-climate","base_path":"/government/ministers/parliamentary-under-secretary-of-state-minister-for-climate","content_id":"6c8ce754-ccfb-4803-a6ee-9c84068ec3b9","details":{"body":"<p>The minister is responsible for:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>international climate and energy policy</li>\n  <li>international climate finance</li>\n  <li>carbon budgets and Net Zero strategy</li>\n  <li>citizen engagement</li>\n  <li>local Net Zero</li>\n  <li>green finance</li>\n  <li>methane emissions</li>\n</ul>\n","role_payment_type":null,"seniority":100,"whip_organisation":{}},"document_type":"ministerial_role","links":{"ordered_parent_organisations":[{"analytics_identifier":"D1380","api_path":"/api/content/government/organisations/department-for-energy-security-and-net-zero","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/organisations/department-for-energy-security-and-net-zero","base_path":"/government/organisations/department-for-energy-security-and-net-zero","content_id":"6315817c-ef11-4905-bb4d-b6dca8e9052c","details":{"acronym":"DESNZ","brand":"department-for-business-innovation-skills","default_news_image":{"high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/656df1fd1104cf000dfa74a1/s960_whitehall-place-exterior-960x640.jpg","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/656df1fd0f12ef07a53e01be/s300_whitehall-place-exterior-960x640.jpg"},"logo":{"crest":"single-identity","formatted_title":"Department for<br/>Energy Security<br/>&amp; Net Zero"},"organisation_govuk_status":{"status":"live","updated_at":null,"url":null}},"document_type":"organisation","links":{},"locale":"en","schema_name":"organisation","title":"Department for Energy Security and Net Zero","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/department-for-energy-security-and-net-zero","withdrawn":false}]},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2025-09-17T11:25:49Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Parliamentary Under-Secretary of State (Minister for Climate)","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/government/ministers/parliamentary-under-secretary-of-state-minister-for-climate","withdrawn":false}]},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2025-09-17T13:16:22Z","schema_name":"role_appointment","title":"Katie White OBE MP - Parliamentary Under-Secretary of State (Minister for Climate)","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"486e263b-151b-405d-9686-2f196f425b7e","details":{"current":false,"ended_on":"2025-09-07T00:00:00+01:00","person_appointment_order":2,"started_on":"2024-07-09T00:00:00+01:00"},"document_type":"role_appointment","links":{"person":[{"api_path":"/api/content/government/people/kerry-mccarthy","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/people/kerry-mccarthy","base_path":"/government/people/kerry-mccarthy","content_id":"70a5dbf1-9dbe-497b-affa-30bceb3f441d","details":{"body":"<p>Kerry McCarthy was Parliamentary Under-Secretary of State at the Department for Energy Security and Net Zero between 9 July 2024 and 7 September 2025. She was elected as the Labour MP for Bristol East in May 2005.</p>\n\n<h3 id=\"education\">Education</h3>\n\n<p>Kerry studied Russian, Politics and Linguistics at the University of Liverpool before studying law at the City of London Polytechnic.</p>\n\n<h3 id=\"political-career\">Political career</h3>\n\n<p>Kerry was Assistant Whip at HM Treasury from 2009 to 2010.</p>\n\n<p>She held several posts while in opposition, including:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>Shadow Minister (Climate Change and Net Zero), 2022 to 2024</li>\n  <li>Shadow Minister (Transport), 2020 to 2021</li>\n  <li>Shadow Secretary of State for Environment, Food and Rural Affairs, 2015 to 2016</li>\n  <li>Shadow Minister (Foreign and Commonwealth Affairs), 2011 to 2015</li>\n  <li>Shadow Minister (Treasury), 2010 to 2011</li>\n  <li>Shadow Minister (Work and Pensions), 2010 to 2010</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>She also served on Luton Borough Council from 1995 to 1996 and 1999 to 2003.</p>\n\n<h3 id=\"career-outside-politics\">Career outside politics</h3>\n\n<p>Kerry qualified as a solicitor in 1994 and worked as a lawyer before becoming involved in politics.</p>\n","image":{"alt_text":"Kerry McCarthy MP","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/6697e062fc8e12ac3edafec8/s465_kerry-mccarthy.jpg"}},"document_type":"person","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2025-09-08T08:07:58Z","schema_name":"person","title":"Kerry McCarthy MP","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/government/people/kerry-mccarthy","withdrawn":false}],"role":[{"api_path":"/api/content/government/ministers/parliamentary-under-secretary-of-state-minister-for-climate","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/ministers/parliamentary-under-secretary-of-state-minister-for-climate","base_path":"/government/ministers/parliamentary-under-secretary-of-state-minister-for-climate","content_id":"6c8ce754-ccfb-4803-a6ee-9c84068ec3b9","details":{"body":"<p>The minister is responsible for:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>international climate and energy policy</li>\n  <li>international climate finance</li>\n  <li>carbon budgets and Net Zero strategy</li>\n  <li>citizen engagement</li>\n  <li>local Net Zero</li>\n  <li>green finance</li>\n  <li>methane emissions</li>\n</ul>\n","role_payment_type":null,"seniority":100,"whip_organisation":{}},"document_type":"ministerial_role","links":{"ordered_parent_organisations":[{"analytics_identifier":"D1380","api_path":"/api/content/government/organisations/department-for-energy-security-and-net-zero","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/organisations/department-for-energy-security-and-net-zero","base_path":"/government/organisations/department-for-energy-security-and-net-zero","content_id":"6315817c-ef11-4905-bb4d-b6dca8e9052c","details":{"acronym":"DESNZ","brand":"department-for-business-innovation-skills","default_news_image":{"high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/656df1fd1104cf000dfa74a1/s960_whitehall-place-exterior-960x640.jpg","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/656df1fd0f12ef07a53e01be/s300_whitehall-place-exterior-960x640.jpg"},"logo":{"crest":"single-identity","formatted_title":"Department for<br/>Energy Security<br/>&amp; Net Zero"},"organisation_govuk_status":{"status":"live","updated_at":null,"url":null}},"document_type":"organisation","links":{},"locale":"en","schema_name":"organisation","title":"Department for Energy Security and Net Zero","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/department-for-energy-security-and-net-zero","withdrawn":false}]},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2025-09-17T11:25:49Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Parliamentary Under-Secretary of State (Minister for Climate)","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/government/ministers/parliamentary-under-secretary-of-state-minister-for-climate","withdrawn":false}]},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2025-09-08T08:08:22Z","schema_name":"role_appointment","title":"Kerry McCarthy MP - Parliamentary Under-Secretary of State (Minister for Climate)","withdrawn":false}]},"locale":"en","phase":"live","public_updated_at":"2025-09-17T12:25:49+01:00","publishin